Introduction

Nina (니나) is a South Korean singer and member of the upcoming girl group Bunny.T under W2 Company.

Back in 2018, Nina debuted as a member of the girl group We Girls but left a year later. Following this, in 2022, she made her official debut, this time as a member of the now-disbanded girl group Bambino.

In 2023, Nina was announced as a member of the upcoming girl group Bunny.T who is set to debut in June.
